{"id":593158,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/08/时间news-民政局给新人发家庭手册：女性露胳膊/","date":"2018-08-17T07:53:31Z","modified":"2018-08-17T07:53:31Z","title":"时间NEWS | 民政局给新人发“家庭手册”：女性露胳膊是作贱自己","content":"<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/cf3c424191eaa6e9f5d4ef905246fdd0.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-593166\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/cf3c424191eaa6e9f5d4ef905246fdd0.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"311\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/cf3c424191eaa6e9f5d4ef905246fdd0.jpg 550w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/cf3c424191eaa6e9f5d4ef905246fdd0-300x170.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>15日 ，河北邯郸，网友称到复兴区民政局领结婚证，发给了她一本名为《家和万事兴》的红色小书，内容看似为“伦理道德，治家之道”，但实质为“歧视女性，挑战医学常识”。 工作人员说书是他人捐赠的，捐赠人具体信息他们均不清楚。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/06c495fa733c663139c9bed9785b366e.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-593161\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/06c495fa733c663139c9bed9785b366e.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"436\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/06c495fa733c663139c9bed9785b366e.jpg 550w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/06c495fa733c663139c9bed9785b366e-300x238.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>有网友称到复兴区民政局领结婚证，工作人员给了她一本名为《家和万事兴》的红色小书。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/daba9c4c4b4ad07b6eec384f525e72a3.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-593168\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/daba9c4c4b4ad07b6eec384f525e72a3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/daba9c4c4b4ad07b6eec384f525e72a3.jpg 550w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/daba9c4c4b4ad07b6eec384f525e72a3-225x300.jpg 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>“姑娘要多干活 少花钱 别嘴馋”</strong></p>\n<p><strong>“姑娘要自重 露腿露胳膊是作贱自己”</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/994a1e20ef4259c1f66d75248b8cc8b0.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-593163\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/994a1e20ef4259c1f66d75248b8cc8b0.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/994a1e20ef4259c1f66d75248b8cc8b0.jpg 550w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/994a1e20ef4259c1f66d75248b8cc8b0-225x300.jpg 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>“姑娘生孩子后得了先天性疾病是因为姑娘性格不好”</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/31261dd5a898a70c4c8bc76990e457b7.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-593164\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/31261dd5a898a70c4c8bc76990e457b7.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/31261dd5a898a70c4c8bc76990e457b7.jpg 550w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/31261dd5a898a70c4c8bc76990e457b7-169x300.jpg 169w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>“订婚要征得父母同意任意而为就是不孝顺父母”</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/fbfd963d872e3fd8e9a04fbae4f26a32.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-593169\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/fbfd963d872e3fd8e9a04fbae4f26a32.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/fbfd963d872e3fd8e9a04fbae4f26a32.jpg 550w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/fbfd963d872e3fd8e9a04fbae4f26a32-225x300.jpg 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>“病是因为有过 都是自己招的”</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/d273ffc51b67c84460d34652885bc617.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-593167\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/d273ffc51b67c84460d34652885bc617.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/d273ffc51b67c84460d34652885bc617.jpg 550w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/d273ffc51b67c84460d34652885bc617-225x300.jpg 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>“腰上的病是夫妻之间生气来的”</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/c0e20ca8ed1e861f69922513ca3f786e.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-593165\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/c0e20ca8ed1e861f69922513ca3f786e.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/c0e20ca8ed1e861f69922513ca3f786e.jpg 550w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/c0e20ca8ed1e861f69922513ca3f786e-225x300.jpg 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/44bc6f664f8e447d10201f97624562b3.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-593162\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/44bc6f664f8e447d10201f97624562b3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/44bc6f664f8e447d10201f97624562b3.jpg 550w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/44bc6f664f8e447d10201f97624562b3-225x300.jpg 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p>复兴区民政局婚姻登记处就此事作出回应，称书本内容为宣扬传统文化，对新婚夫妇有帮助。工作人员解释书本是下半年有人捐赠的，捐赠人所属机构和联系方式他们均不清楚。当时捐赠人留下二三十本书，发放之后目前还剩下十几本。</p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,20534],"tags":[13379,35758,26991,35759,35757,14293,34680,21929,35760]}